msgid "Scenario VI: Return to The City of Archives"
msgstr "冒险VI：重返天机之城"

msgid "Put the four Halls of Pnakotus locations into play (the 3 from the original set and the new Halls of Pnakotus <i>(Southern Corridors)</i>). Set each remaining location aside, out of play."
msgstr "将4个纳克特廊道地点放置入场(3张来自原本的遭遇组，以及1张新的纳克特廊道<i>(南翼通道)</i>)。将所有剩余地点放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "When instructed to put locations into play during act 1b, put Cyclopean Vaults and Alien Conservatory into play as well."
msgstr "在场景1b指示将地点放置入场时，将巨大密库和异形展室一起放置入场。"

msgid "Remove Act 2a—\"Restricted Access\" from the game and replace it with the new Act 2a—\"Unrestricted Access.\""
msgstr "将场景2a——“禁止通行”从游戏中移除，用新版的场景2a——“自由通行”替换。"

msgid "Because at least 6 tasks were completed, record in your Campaign Log that <i>the process was perfected</i>. Each investigator earns 4 bonus experience as they gain insight into the secrets of the Earth."
msgstr "因为至少完成了6个任务，在冒险日志中记录<i>归位程式完美完成</i>。调查员得知了地球的秘密，每位调查员获得4点奖励经验值。"
